      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a deep, mirror-like finish on its original factory paint with absolutely zero swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather bolsters are firm and uncreased, the carpets are spotless, and the interior retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, it performs with the precision of a new car, having been maintained strictly according to manufacturer schedules with a complete, organized binder of service records to prove it. From the pristine alloy wheels with no curb rash to the spotless undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a benchmark example. Fully documented and ready for immediate delivery.",
